import axios from"axios";import{GET_PROFILE,PROFILE_ERROR}from'./types';//Get current users profile 
export const getCurrentProfile=()=>async dispatch=>{try{const res=await axios.get('./api/profile/me');dispatch({type:GET_PROFILE,payload:res.data});}catch(error){dispatch({type:PROFILE_ERROR,payload:{msg:error.response.statusText,status:error.response.status}});}};
